    "Here are some of the related works in Arabic Dialectal machine translation and unsupervised machine translation related work:",
    "In this paper 9, They are proposing algorithms that try to overcome the limitations of low-resource languages and apply them to translate Egyptian dialects (EGY) to Modern Standard Arabic (MSA).",
    "For both MSA and EGY, monolingual corpora were collected, and a relatively small parallel language pair set was created to train the models.",
    "Because it requires monolingual data rather than a parallel corpus, the proposed method employs Word embedding.",
    "To create word vectors, both Continuous Bag of Words and Skip-gram were used, Word2vec by 10."
